Static route for network engineers:

R4: route 10.1.1.4 /30 and 10.1.1.0/30

1stHop: 10.1.1.9

conf t
ip route 10.1.1.4 255.255.255.252 10.1.1.9 1
ip route 10.1.1.0 255.255.255.252 10.1.1.9 1

